'''Ferhat Mehenni''', d aselway n [[Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt n i Kvayeliyen|Umussu i Timanit n Tmurt n i Kvayliyen]] (M.A.K.), ilul-d deg [[5 Meγres]] [[1951]] deg taddart n Illula, deg tama n temdinin n [[Buzegan]], [[Iaezzugen]], akk-d [[Akbu]]. 

Asmi i d-kemmel almad-ines deg Tesdawit n [[Lezzayer]] (tamaneγt) yevda-d tikli-ines di ccna deg 1973 imi yewwi tarrazt tamezwarut n tafaska tatrart n ccna n Lezzayer. 
Kra n wukud sin akkin isbeggen-d iman-is d akken yella mgal unabad n iɣil n Lezzayer imi yevda-d avrid n tigwin; γef igiten agi yekcem-d γer temufrikt 13 iverdan.

Sakin (sin akkin)[[Tafsut Taverkant]], imi Tamselta n Lezzayer tenγa yiwen weqcic amelsi yettusemman [[Masinisa Germah]], Ferhat Mhenni isbed ''Amussu i Timanit n Tmurt''; tuddsa ixeddmen akken a tessiwed ar timanit n tmurt n yekvayliyen. Llan wid i nnan d akken γef demma n wannecta i yettwanγa mmi-s Amezian Mehenni deg 2004, di Tamanaγt n Fransa, Paris.

Amussu i Timanit n Tamurt (MAK), [[Agraw i Yedles d Tugdut]] (RCD), akk-d [[Tirni Iγallen Inemlayen]] (FFS) d ikabaren isertiyen i lin (sann) azal deg [[Tamurt n el Kvayel|Tmurt n Izwawen]].

